          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two Experiments were performed at each energy - One",
                "covering the angular interval 0-90 degrees and the",
                "other 90-108 degrees relative to the beam.",
                "The thin target was prepared by evaporating enriched",
                "Cu-65 (99.7%) and Au-197 on to Aluminium backing",
                "material.The target thickness for Gold and Copper were",
                "3-7 and 4-8 mug/cm**2 respectively and the target",
                "dimensions were 0.8 cm*1.2 cm.The collection radius and",
                "collector height were 9.53 and 5.08 cm, respectively.",
                "To avoid any difference in the target thickness in the",
                "forward and backward experiments at same energy, two",
                "sections of the same target prepared were used for both",
                "experiments.",
                "Three identical Aluminium foils were used on the",
                "collector mount, the first for recoil collection, the",
                "second for activation correction and the third to",
                "compensate for the recoils from the Aluminium mount to",
                "the blank foil."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
