          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PROPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A Low-Background Proportional Counter."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".Monte Carlo evaporation calculations, cascade-",
                "evaporation calculations at 85 MeV for Cu-64 and",
                "inelastic scattering plus evaporation calculations.",
                "Scattering effect of the recoils due to the orientation",
                "of the target (90 degrees) to the incident proton beam",
                "was reported."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*by Authors*.Preliminary Experiments were Conducted For",
                "The Purpose of Ascertaining the Extent of Scattering of",
                "Low Energy Recoils and Impurity Activation in the",
                "Backing and Catcher Materials.The Scattering Effect is",
                "Mainly Due to Angular Orientation of the Target with",
                "Respect to the Proton Beam,Target Thickness,the Effect",
                "Of the Backing Material.",
                "The Data Corrected For Dilution,Chemical Yield,Self-",
                "Absorption and Back-Scattering of Electron were Treated",
                "As Follows-",
                "Extrapolation to Angular Regions For Which Collection",
                "Was not Made Directly.",
                "Interpolation at 90 Degree and Matching of the Data",
                "From the Forward-Backward Experiments to Get a",
                "Continuous Curve.",
                "Normalization of the Total Activity to the Same Value",
                " (10000 C.P.M.)",
                "Calculation of an Average Angle For Each Distribution",
                "At a Definite Energy."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The Errors in the Angular Distribution",
                "Measurements Involve the Errors Associated with the",
                "Resolution of the Decay Curves, the Counter Background,",
                "Chemical Yields, Weights of the Target and",
                "Nonuniformities of the Target and Catcher Thickness,",
                "The Scattering of the Low- Energy Recoiling Nuclides,",
                "Dilution Factors, Radio-Chemical Purity,",
                "Self-Absorption and Back-Scattering of the Beta",
                "Radiation in the Sample.  The Estimated Error Amounted",
                "To 9% For Copper and 14% For Gold Isotopes."
              ]
            }
          ],
